Wizards have the ability "Harvest of Druzzil" that gathers them mana, re-useable every 12 minutes.  Do wizards get by and seldom go OOM before getting this ability?  Yes, but once they have it and know they can rely on it do they readjust their tactics to incorporate it?  yes.  
<br />

<br />
I say that a group knowing they were going to be receiveing a PoS every 15 minutes could adjust their tactics to incorportate it in such a way, that they can kill more things, in less time, that somehow corresponds to a very rough value of 6k damage over 15 minutes.  It's difficult to evaluate such things completely.
